助。 自上台以来，尹锡悦政府以加强韩美同盟和韩美日合作为主的外交政策，但在其上任不到一年的时间里，其对日和对美外交政策已饱受诟病。对日方面，韩日第 12 次安全政策协商会议于本月 17 日在首尔举行，这是时隔 5 年之后的首次重启。在之前的 11 日，韩国外交部刚刚召见日本公使，对日本《外交蓝皮书》主张拥有独岛（日本称竹岛）主权表示强烈抗议。对美方面，媒体曝光美方曾对韩国国安室等部门进行监听窃听，有韩国高官 13 日「急于平息风波」地表示，并无证据表明美曾对韩进行监听窃听。 尹锡悦称可能向乌提供军援，外媒：首次改变韩国向乌供武立场"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-bef2378b07c925672e9ef3351f80c4d6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596530043"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI56TV/vHQ4d1gEAMaCDk0ODQzMjQzIJWx/qEGMAQ4fEAecgk1OTY1MzAwNDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1681957504.701361", "card_id": "Q_593687585", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "男生总熬夜皮肤干还有细纹，有哪些护肤好习惯可以打造健康活力的皮肤状态？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "男生经常熬夜，最近感觉面部很干燥甚至出现了小细纹，求问下同胞们怎么护肤的呀？有哪些护肤习惯分享下啊～"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1a7e42c1484223e23aa74618a32a6437_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593687585"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I56TV/vHQ4d1gEAMaCDk0MjEyMTg5IJG6sKEGMAE4kwFAH3IJNTkzNjg3NTg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1681957504.701828", "card_id": "Q_590341406", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "徒步登山如果陷入险境如迷路、山洪、掉落悬崖等，如何自救？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-91ed0f22a4fd95fc4368e010c0443048_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "